Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.70,0:01:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,創界山是分了七層\N由神僊居住的山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了打倒支配這座山的\N邪惡帝皇多惡達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.90,0:01:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們向第七界層前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.84,0:01:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把前六個界層\N恢復了原狀的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.60,0:01:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在上第七界層途中\N迷失在一個叫魔幻境的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.25,0:01:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非通過四道\N魔幻地獄門不可的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.42,0:01:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和火美子在第二道門\N魔風門內要解開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.76,0:02:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,守門人馬鹿提出的三條難題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.86,0:02:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題雖然是又要唱歌\N又要捉風的怪問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.56,0:02:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我和火美子\N合力把三條難題解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再把馬鹿的魔神\N骷髏惡魔打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.87,0:02:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,跟著是第三道門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.41,0:02:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.14,0:02:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三十五話\N升到天上去!魔天門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.56,0:02:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了\N四處也看不見魔天門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.10,0:02:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟能來到這裏呢\N但只能到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.00,0:02:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?出來!麻婆\N真卑鄙,你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.57,0:02:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別嚇人啊,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.98,0:03:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看吧,這是第三道\N魔幻地獄門,魔天門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.47,0:03:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不趕快的話\N人質就會死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用你說我也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.60,0:03:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的啊\N喂!你不要過來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.60,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛!我的頭啊\N父親!大叔!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.14,0:03:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N渡怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二道門也通過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.47,0:03:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做得好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.98,0:04:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼請你們\N等待下一次報告吧,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!火美子,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救我們出去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用指望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.20,0:04:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪了,從剛才起就好像\N在同一地方不斷繞圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.27,0:04:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去了…掉下去了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,腳可以碰地的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.37,0:05:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏真的是魔天門裏面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.27,0:05:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得對\N但這裏是魔天門的最底層呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.85,0:05:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.72,0:05:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我嗎?\N我是魔天門的帶路者迪布路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好好記著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪布路嗎?我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.39,0:05:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有,你掉進了這裏\N就不能再回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.13,0:05:28.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看看上面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.60,0:05:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出口只有那處啊\N什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.18,0:05:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只這樣\N在你身邊的人全都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.55,0:05:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想打倒多惡達\N而掉進這裏的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.50,0:05:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?但是大家也好像\N很悠閒地休息的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.59,0:05:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為就算出去也去不了去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,要你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子\N你為什麼會在這裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.94,0:06:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看見渡進入了水洼內\N所以就追來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.61,0:06:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我不喜歡這裏啊\N渡,快點出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.98,0:06:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是那個水洼是出口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害!厲害!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.42,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你明白我的意思嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,適可而止啊!\N竟在人家背上一直站著不走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是站,是坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.07,0:06:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不可愛的小鬼呢\N不准鬥嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有鬥嘴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.08,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住口!住口!…\N反正你們也不能出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.48,0:06:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏\N悠閒地好好生活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們為什麼悠閒地喝茶啊\N有這樣空閒嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.49,0:07:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你叫我們悠閒地生活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.93,0:07:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要人叫做什麼\N就立即做什麼,知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,登上那座山\N也許可以走出這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真蠢\N你以為能登上那座山嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.59,0:07:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧,你要上就隨便你\N雖然我想是絕不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.46,0:07:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能不可能還未做過怎知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還未到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.61,0:07:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,加油…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.82,0:08:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那精力從哪裏走出來的\N我不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.96,0:08:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘩!是丸子店啊\N在哪?真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.77,0:08:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要丸子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.64,0:08:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎光臨,請慢慢休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.71,0:08:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經在休息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?丸子到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.12,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我吃飽了\N好吃嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,婆婆,我還想要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.89,0:08:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼想要,看看碟子後面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碟子後面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.63,0:08:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些字寫著啊\N"回到起點"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是回到原來的地方的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.56,0:09:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歡迎回來\N迪布路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.26,0:09:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丸子的味道怎樣?\N只要掉進這裏就不能再出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.10,0:09:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,爬牆之術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.22,0:09:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒是你好像爬得很辛苦呢\N渡,一想到這裏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.26,0:09:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!前面還有這麼高呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.37,0:09:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是時候放棄比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.14,0:10:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以!\N誰會放棄啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.40,0:10:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?\N啊!這下不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.55,0:10:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是雷聲\N不對,是塌山泥的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.02,0:10:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝你好運了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塌山泥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.77,0:10:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,二人三足跳躍術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,著陸成功!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.38,0:10:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你未死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.95,0:10:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總算是呢\N但是剛才的撞擊…很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.50,0:11:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,避雷針之術\N這樣就不怕閃電了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.54,0:11:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好癢啊\N可…可怕的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.36,0:11:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是…成功了,到山頂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,渡!\N萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.30,0:12:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,這麼辛苦才上來\N卻沒有用呢,是時候放棄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這點小事我會放棄嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.80,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是樓梯,用它上去\N也許可以到達出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真是頑強的傢伙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.58,0:12:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,只要還有一點氣力\N也要上去,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.35,0:12:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,如你走得很慢\N我就留下你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.02,0:12:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子…等等我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.80,0:12:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,奮鬥!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.91,0:12:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已…到極限了,放棄!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.75,0:13:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你醒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.36,0:13:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,怎麼了?好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.66,0:13:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡放棄之後樓梯就消失了\N這次比剛才掉得更低呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.34,0:13:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又掉下來了,渡\N怎樣?還要幹嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.15,0:13:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?\N那我告訴你一個好消息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.52,0:13:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天上的洞會隨著時間關閉\N如關上就不會再打開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天上的洞會關?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.83,0:13:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…快點回來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.67,0:13:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連叫的氣力也沒有\N渡到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.44,0:14:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡…渡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.75,0:14:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,奮鬥!\N渡,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.62,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子美子美子\N渡,加油!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.76,0:14:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論怎爬,結果也是掉下來\N幹什麼也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.80,0:14:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是誰走這麼長的樓梯\N也會中途放棄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你有精神了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我聽到火美子\N你的打氣聲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.61,0:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是忍法,變精神之舞啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.88,0:14:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火美子,你剛才說我放棄時\N樓梯就消失了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.55,0:14:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.70,0:14:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是這樣\N這裏是不可以放棄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.79,0:14:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要想著要幹些什麼\N而不干到最後就會返回原處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.83,0:14:55.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我要再挑戰多一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.07,0:15:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了創界山的各人\N還有為了師傅和世伯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,用這個爬上去\N就能出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.10,0:15:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你們在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪布路\N我知道這個世界的秘密了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.13,0:15:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?不可以放棄\N絕對不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.77,0:15:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個…渡先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你看看下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.51,0:15:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了,這條繩很快會斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.50,0:15:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?\N啊,那個洞變小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎…怎會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.19,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,怎麼辦?\N現在繩斷了再掉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.89,0:16:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就不會再有第二次機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.16,0:16:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這條繩斷了的話…\N繩斷了的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.37,0:16:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!變細了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就快斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要放棄…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.30,0:16:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.93,0:16:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會放棄的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.54,0:16:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.27,0:16:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變粗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話…\N這樣的繩讓我咬斷它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.73,0:17:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!\N萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.09,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,接著只剩下尋找出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.30,0:17:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你竟能回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.57,0:17:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然了,我絕對不會放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.74,0:17:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這番話留待打倒了\N魔天門的守護魔神再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.58,0:17:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出現了嗎?好!\N來吧!龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.10,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯呢,龍神丸\N用炎龍拳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.85,0:18:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸,快離開它\N好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想…想幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.27,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…龍神丸,就這樣\N掉進那些針山我們死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,我的力量不夠擺脫它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.10,0:19:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以放棄的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.32,0:19:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸的!\N來吧,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.20,0:19:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,力量全開!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.70,0:19:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變身!龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形!鳳凰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.10,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,這次到我們進攻了\N龍王丸,用鳳雷炮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.54,0:20:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.50,0:20:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,這樣就用接近戰\N變形!龍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.58,0:20:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.37,0:20:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會中同一招式嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了!\N劍被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.56,0:20:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍王丸,可惡!\N有沒有可以用的東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.10,0:20:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那個了,龍王丸!\N把它撞向那邊的岩石吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.57,0:20:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.75,0:20:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了!\N龍王丸,跳吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.75,0:20:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用這個刺向它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,取回劍吧!龍王丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧!渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.10,0:21:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.50,0:21:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳳龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.13,0:21:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,第三條鑰匙也到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.83,0:21:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,很精彩\N你竟然從那洞內逃出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.00,0:21:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已不會再放棄了\N絕對會通過這魔幻地獄門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.94,0:21:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣了,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.98,0:21:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.80,0:22:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後的魔幻地獄門是魔界門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.00,0:22:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你絕對不能通過

